327
00:15:06,029 --> 00:15:07,490
What's a roguelike, what's a deck builder, right?

328
00:15:09,011 --> 00:15:11,332
Compound this with the fact that we have no reputation

329
00:15:11,372 --> 00:15:14,973
as game developers besides these failure games from the past.

330
00:15:16,102 --> 00:15:18,904
and so much more new game developers were entering the space.

331
00:15:19,624 --> 00:15:21,705
Engines like Unity were lowering the barrier to entry

332
00:15:21,925 --> 00:15:23,265
for developers, and this is great,

333
00:15:24,426 --> 00:15:26,007
but that meant we were also all competing

