00:15:46,801 --> 00:15:48,422
and it's fun, and we got all the things that we wanted.

343
00:15:49,502 --> 00:15:52,224
Two, all of our friends, which we invited

344
00:15:52,244 --> 00:15:53,604
into our secret playtesting group,

345
00:15:54,085 --> 00:15:54,845
were having a great time.

346
00:15:56,126 --> 00:15:57,406
They were having a really great time.

