00:35:21,062 --> 00:35:22,303
so everyone actually read those announcements,

784
00:35:22,323 --> 00:35:23,083
which was fantastic.

785
00:35:23,908 --> 00:35:25,369
Whenever we posted announcements on Steam,

786
00:35:25,770 --> 00:35:28,051
it would be cross-posted to places like Discord,

787
00:35:28,891 --> 00:35:30,252
Twitter, and our Facebook channels.

