00:36:34,908 --> 00:36:37,990
ask them to email us at support at megacrit.com.

817
00:36:38,790 --> 00:36:41,212
If we wanted to talk about the game or work on localization,

818
00:36:41,832 --> 00:36:43,133
we'd be exchanging files all the time.

819
00:36:43,593 --> 00:36:44,734
That was usually done in Discord.

