1300
00:57:33,870 --> 00:57:36,611
And I was just saving up money while I was working on Amazon

1301
00:57:37,071 --> 00:57:39,093
and it was just out of pocket between Anthony and I.

1302
00:57:40,954 --> 00:57:48,018
What the budget is, I think we did different types of models

1303
00:57:48,378 --> 00:57:50,619
