1304
00:57:51,953 --> 00:57:53,213
on a per contractor basis.

1305
00:57:53,893 --> 00:57:55,234
And how did you determine that number?

1306
00:57:55,454 --> 00:57:58,115
I don't know.

1307
00:57:58,275 --> 00:58:01,816
I think for each one we did a bunch of research in general.

1308
00:58:01,976 --> 00:58:09,558
We also actually, we used game dev classifieds on Reddit and Gamasutra, and then we just

1309
00:58:09,598 --> 00:58:11,518
