1310
00:58:12,079 --> 00:58:13,479
So I think it's up to...

1311
00:58:14,914 --> 00:58:17,935
Interviewing is a very interesting process, and it's very important.

1312
00:58:18,195 --> 00:58:22,136
I don't think you should ever go for the first person that you get.

1313
00:58:22,356 --> 00:58:28,057
We went over several different people for each contractor, at least 10 illustrators

1314
00:58:28,097 --> 00:58:30,238
