1324
00:58:58,965 --> 00:59:01,246
where a lot of people wanted to hack the game to add content

1325
00:59:01,606 --> 00:59:04,088
because maybe we weren't working hard enough, I'm not sure.

1326
00:59:04,668 --> 00:59:06,009
But it happened that way,

1327
00:59:06,269 --> 00:59:08,851
and then the stuff that came out of it was incredible.

1328
00:59:09,331 --> 00:59:11,412
And so we were like, this is modding now,

1329
00:59:11,693 --> 00:59:15,295
and we had a channel for almost a year and a half,

1330
00:59:15,555 --> 00:59:16,676
well I guess how long was the development?

1331
00:59:17,056 --> 00:59:19,777
A year and a few months, called Unsupported Modding.

1332
00:59:19,958 --> 00:59:21,198
It was called Unsupported Modding,

1333
00:59:21,278 --> 00:59:22,999
