1345
00:59:52,769 --> 00:59:53,469
It's kind of weird.

1346
00:59:54,110 --> 00:59:54,730
It just happened.

1347
00:59:56,111 --> 00:59:56,231
So.

1348
00:59:57,177 --> 00:59:58,538
That's the story of our modding, I guess.

1349
00:59:59,038 --> 01:00:00,099
It's very important, I think.

1350
01:00:00,599 --> 01:00:03,260
The mods are incredible, and it's been really good.

1351
01:00:04,080 --> 01:00:04,561
Awesome, thanks.

